---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="Cookie Policy of Campeonato Pasos Libres: how we use cookies and how you can manage them."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="container legal-inner">
      <h1 class="script-title">Cookies Policy</h1>

      <p>
        At Campeonato Pasos Libres (www.campeonatopasoslibres.com), we use cookies to enhance the user
        experience, analyze site traffic and deliver personalized content. We want to make sure you
        understand how we use cookies and how you can manage them.
      </p>

      <h2>What are cookies?</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit a website. These files
        allow the website to remember information about your browsing, such as your preferences or logged in
        session, to improve your user experience.
      </p>

      <h2>What types of cookies do we use?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> These are necessary for the operation of the website and cannot
          be disabled on our systems. Without them, some basic functions, such as navigation or access to
          secure areas, may not be available.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analytics and performance cookies:</strong> They help us understand how users interact with
          our website, allowing us to improve its performance. We use tools such as Google Analytics to
          collect usage data anonymously.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> These cookies allow us to remember your preferences and
          personalize your experience on the site.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Advertising and social media cookies:</strong> These are used to display relevant ads based
          on your interests and to allow you to share content on social networks.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cookie management</h2>
      <p>
        When you visit our site for the first time, we show you a cookie notice where you can accept all
        cookies, reject them or set your preferences. At any time, you can modify your consent through the
        cookie settings on our website or in your browser settings.
      </p>
      <p>Here are the links to manage cookies in the most popular browsers:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647?hl=es" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Google Chrome
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://support.mozilla.org/es/kb/Borrar%20cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Mozilla Firefox
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://support.microsoft.com/es-es/microsoft-edge/ver-y-eliminar-las-cookies-en-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            Microsoft Edge
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://support.apple.com/es-es/HT201265" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Safari</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        For more information on how third parties may handle your data and the transfer of your data, please
        see our <a href="/en/privacy-policy/">privacy policy</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We may use third party services that collect information through cookies, such as Google Analytics or
        social media tools. These providers may transfer data outside the European Economic Area. We ensure
        that they comply with applicable regulations and take appropriate protection measures.
      </p>

      <h2>Modifications in the cookies policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy at any time based on legal changes or improvements to our services. We
        encourage you to review it periodically.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our cookie policy, you can write to us at
        <a href="mailto:info@lanegrasalsa.com">info@lanegrasalsa.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal {
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .legal-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
    margin: 40px 0 14px;
  }
  .legal p {
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }
  .legal ul {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .legal li {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .legal a {
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
